{"tid":1746260,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"區選又黎番射落海都唔益泛民？","createTime":"2019-11-22T16:06:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T16:41:21.000Z","uid":10080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f9aad5091d6b793e4bc57f084999f71f1b0563ad","tid":1746260,"uid":10080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T16:06:02.000Z","msg":"2015 既區議會選舉 大家都話射落海唔益泛民。黎都2019年今次既區選仲黎依一套？<br />\n<br />\n仲射落海都唔益泛民， <span style=\"color: red;\">最後咪又係益左班建制</span>！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">今次既區選，就係比政府，比全香港，比全世界，甚至你地最想佢地幫我地既國際社會知道我地既民意係邊一邊。</span><br />\n<br />\n要所有人知道民意係邊一邊，今次投票就係我地最有力既一次機會黎表達比人地睇。<br />\n<br />\n你話615, 每一次既遊行都有幾多人幾萬人出黎遊行，<span style=\"color: red;\">但果d 數字都係大家估算出黎</span><span style=\"color: red;\">，但今次投票就係最大既民意調查，顯示比人睇我地香港人依經歷依五個月既痛苦，我地就五大訴求既堅持都係不變既。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">今次既投票結果就係我地最大去武器黎去用。</span><br />\n香港方面，可以比政府知道佢地既所謂民知係邊一邊。<span style=\"color: red;\">唔洗比佢地再用d 廢話黎話沉默既大多數呃人。</span><br />\n<br />\n外國方面，<span style=\"color: red;\">外國最重視既就係民主投票黎結果</span>。今次既結果係最大既武器比到外國睇我地香港既民意係點。<span style=\"color: red;\">要d 咩法案過，人地都可以捉住今次既結果黎去傾。</span><br />\n<br />\n所以依家我地一地要捉住我地<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">講左五個月既不分化 不割席 不篤灰</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不分和勇 獨自爬山</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我地咩都唔做就係幫緊建制</span><br />\n<br />\n大家記住星期日一定要早d 去投票<br />\n投票過程有d 咩人攪事破壞都由佢地，等全香港完成左場投票先再算。<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<br />\n香港人報仇！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gt6SiJ8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgt6SiJ8.jpg&h=eccd4109&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0SPo9QP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0SPo9QP.jpg&h=11969c20&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vFXYYKa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvFXYYKa.jpg&h=66785d73&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b1c6244ec602b89089b65fa7b23f8ab7a596b1cb","tid":1746260,"uid":10080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T16:08:25.000Z","msg":"721 821 1001 1111<br />\n死左，失蹤既手足<br />\n中大，理大過左咁多日既手足<br />\n<br />\n以上既事都只係岩岩發生，今次既投票都唔行出黎投票都唔行出黎，仲講d 咩要香港人贏？"},{"pid":"bb222b803d14b2eed5262d059f04827746873b5a","tid":1746260,"uid":10080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T16:08:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6b9b3dfd036050166bc773644e66ef2022abdf6f","tid":1746260,"uid":10080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T16:08:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"474281794c6f09e5fb96e30f4fd502de6f975559","tid":1746260,"uid":10080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T16:09:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d8b32d2cea464dd238ba930ce72a8f905b70b3b6","tid":1746260,"uid":10080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T16:09:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a0cebf45a73c577896ee7f551e5d3467d052de14","tid":1746260,"uid":10080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T16:09:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"00e054210951d5b41cf19b1c6e688563e3616d8d","tid":1746260,"uid":10080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T16:09:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7a52ecf49449fa788002c8637306469dee70c4ea","tid":1746260,"uid":10080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T16:09:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab54992e9b6b789e2f8e60e1ffb62e0020f9a993","tid":1746260,"uid":10080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T16:09:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1bbd730e4d6b91f97adcbfde82032eea445881ee","tid":1746260,"uid":10080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T16:10:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"63146064cbd533ccd8b5b0e41eaa612087467e04","tid":1746260,"uid":10080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T16:10:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"182144b215d1d95e91a1ecc8c01d3310baf6258d","tid":1746260,"uid":10080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0